info.name: Diced
info.attribution: The game layout and images (including the library image) were done by https://www.reddit.com/user/96LawDawg and are released to the Public Domain by CC0. The dice are VirtualTabletop assets.
info.description: Roll colored and white dice to mark off scoresheet with boxes of 2-12 trying to get as many boxes as possible.  Highest score wins.
